WEBVTT

00:00:54.799 --> 00:00:55.320
Hello, Sis.

00:00:56.880 --> 00:00:57.479
I'm almost there.

00:00:57.640 --> 00:00:58.320
I'm on my way.

00:00:59.079 --> 00:01:00.320
Okay, bye-bye.

00:01:02.920 --> 00:01:04.920
Who's the old flame you're talking to?

00:01:06.519 --> 00:01:07.280
Give my phone back.

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:09.439
It's you, you witch.

00:01:09.640 --> 00:01:11.079
Snitching to the teacher,

00:01:11.319 --> 00:01:13.120
saying I bully and rob people, huh?

00:01:13.439 --> 00:01:14.439
I'll say it one more time.

00:01:15.079 --> 00:01:15.840
Give my phone back.

00:01:16.079 --> 00:01:17.159
I knew it was you.

00:01:17.560 --> 00:01:19.480
Relying on your family's power and status,

00:01:19.599 --> 00:01:21.040
looking for trouble with me for no reason.

00:01:22.159 --> 00:01:23.159
But don't forget,

00:01:23.719 --> 00:01:25.400
my dad is also a man with some power.

00:01:25.760 --> 00:01:26.519
You...

00:01:28.719 --> 00:01:29.519
Who in school doesn't know

00:01:29.560 --> 00:01:31.439
you're an adopted bastard?

00:01:32.079 --> 00:01:33.560
Today, on behalf of your parents,

00:01:33.719 --> 00:01:34.920
I'm going to teach you a good lesson.

00:01:37.480 --> 00:01:38.120
Run, quick! Run!

00:01:44.280 --> 00:01:45.120
I'm warning you.

00:01:46.040 --> 00:01:47.640
If you dare touch Li Ran again,

00:01:47.920 --> 00:01:49.319
I'll send you to hell.

00:01:59.120 --> 00:02:00.760
How could your sister use a knife to hurt someone?

00:02:01.200 --> 00:02:02.319
That could kill someone.

00:02:04.519 --> 00:02:05.280
Li Ran.

00:02:05.760 --> 00:02:08.039
We didn't object to you seeing Li Ren,

00:02:08.680 --> 00:02:10.479
but she is just too reckless.

00:02:11.280 --> 00:02:13.240
In the past few years, things like this

00:02:13.400 --> 00:02:14.840
have happened several times.

00:02:15.280 --> 00:02:17.319
You are not allowed to contact each other anymore.

00:02:17.800 --> 00:02:18.560
Phone confiscated.

00:02:19.560 --> 00:02:20.199
Do you hear me?

00:02:35.400 --> 00:02:37.199
But you didn't listen to your adoptive parents' advice.

00:02:37.800 --> 00:02:38.840
You created an email account,

00:02:39.759 --> 00:02:41.080
and through the trash folder in the email,

00:02:41.240 --> 00:02:42.080
you communicated with each other.

00:02:44.240 --> 00:02:45.639
Your adoptive father was also a Superintendent.

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:48.280
In order not to pry into your privacy,

00:02:49.159 --> 00:02:50.520
he chose to turn a blind eye.

00:02:52.080 --> 00:02:52.680
If he had earlier

00:02:52.800 --> 00:02:53.960
discovered your chat logs,

00:02:56.159 --> 00:02:57.800
perhaps this tragedy could have been prevented.

00:02:59.439 --> 00:03:00.280
If...

00:03:01.599 --> 00:03:03.520
there aren't that many "ifs" in this world.

00:03:08.280 --> 00:03:09.719
The best performance this month

00:03:10.159 --> 00:03:11.360
still belongs to Di Fu.

00:03:12.280 --> 00:03:13.800
She's only been a Supervisor for two months.

00:03:15.759 --> 00:03:16.479
Learn from her.

00:03:20.120 --> 00:03:20.639
Brother.

00:03:21.080 --> 00:03:23.000
The ones she kidnaps are all influencers.

00:03:23.439 --> 00:03:25.080
Even the ones controlled by her downlines,

00:03:25.280 --> 00:03:26.919
every one of them has top-notch looks and figures.

00:03:27.560 --> 00:03:28.840
If you assign people like that to me,

00:03:29.199 --> 00:03:30.400
I can achieve results like that too.

00:03:30.560 --> 00:03:32.800
She found those people herself.

00:03:33.280 --> 00:03:35.360
And they are very difficult to manage.

00:03:36.240 --> 00:03:37.080
Even if I gave them to you,

00:03:37.639 --> 00:03:39.159
you might not do as well as she does.

00:03:39.919 --> 00:03:41.080
Brother, give me... Enough.

00:03:41.240 --> 00:03:41.840
You may leave.

00:03:44.639 --> 00:03:45.159
Go on. Di Fu, you stay.

00:03:45.280 --> 00:03:45.719
Go.

00:03:51.560 --> 00:03:53.240
This management manual you wrote for me,

00:03:54.199 --> 00:03:54.800
I've read it.

00:03:55.919 --> 00:03:56.520
Not bad.

00:03:59.560 --> 00:04:00.719
Actually, I've also thought about

00:04:01.120 --> 00:04:02.599
wanting to clean up parts of the business.

00:04:04.240 --> 00:04:04.960
Or rather,

00:04:05.479 --> 00:04:07.919
I want to establish a positive image as an entrepreneur.

00:04:09.080 --> 00:04:10.280
So I need a...

00:04:11.400 --> 00:04:12.120
smart,

00:04:13.080 --> 00:04:13.759
beautiful,

00:04:14.719 --> 00:04:15.840
woman who can help me handle things,

00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:16.959
to coordinate with me.

00:04:17.839 --> 00:04:19.199
Whatever orders you have,

00:04:20.040 --> 00:04:21.199
I will do my utmost.

00:04:22.720 --> 00:04:23.399
Very good.

00:04:24.839 --> 00:04:25.879
So I plan to

00:04:26.439 --> 00:04:27.399
give you a promotion.

00:04:29.800 --> 00:04:30.680
Marry me.

00:04:36.680 --> 00:04:37.959
Whatever orders you have,

00:04:39.000 --> 00:04:40.279
I will do my utmost.

00:04:46.920 --> 00:04:47.959
People in our line of work

00:04:48.040 --> 00:04:49.240
are walking a tightrope.

00:04:49.519 --> 00:04:51.160
One slip and we're beyond redemption.

00:04:51.399 --> 00:04:52.120
To survive,

00:04:52.319 --> 00:04:53.279
one must not only be smart,

00:04:53.439 --> 00:04:54.439
but even more ruthless.

00:04:55.079 --> 00:04:56.519
I chose you to be my wife

00:04:56.920 --> 00:04:59.079
because I'm choosing you as my most important partner.

00:04:59.519 --> 00:05:01.519
I value that you are more ruthless than others,

00:05:01.639 --> 00:05:02.600
and more obedient.

00:05:03.560 --> 00:05:06.600
Don't let me down in the future.

00:05:17.240 --> 00:05:17.879
How is it?

00:05:18.800 --> 00:05:21.199
This will be your home from now on.

00:05:21.920 --> 00:05:22.839
My wife.

00:05:24.560 --> 00:05:25.319
It's quite nice.

00:05:29.240 --> 00:05:30.160
Do you know why

00:05:30.199 --> 00:05:32.720
I want to name this house the Tower of Babel?

00:05:37.800 --> 00:05:39.040
The people living in the tower

00:05:39.839 --> 00:05:41.439
are bent on reaching heaven

00:05:41.560 --> 00:05:42.560
and escaping suffering.

00:05:44.600 --> 00:05:46.079
But what they don't know is

00:05:47.160 --> 00:05:50.319
God has already seized them by the throat

00:05:51.240 --> 00:05:53.120
and controls their life and death.

00:05:54.480 --> 00:05:55.120
Tell me,

00:05:56.959 --> 00:05:58.240
in this situation,

00:05:59.120 --> 00:06:00.319
should the people living in the tower

00:06:00.879 --> 00:06:01.920
accept their fate?

00:06:05.079 --> 00:06:06.079
Not only accept their fate,

00:06:07.319 --> 00:06:08.600
but they should also worship

00:06:09.079 --> 00:06:10.680
and make offerings to the God in the sky.

00:06:12.199 --> 00:06:15.560
Because humans cannot fight against the God in the sky.

00:06:18.519 --> 00:06:19.079
Come.

00:06:23.959 --> 00:06:25.879
Just stay obediently in the tower from now on

00:06:26.839 --> 00:06:28.399
and be my wife.

00:06:30.920 --> 00:06:31.920
No matter what you have been through,

00:06:32.040 --> 00:06:33.600
it is no excuse for murder.

00:06:33.720 --> 00:06:36.000
You have no idea how much thought I put into this,

00:06:36.480 --> 00:06:37.800
how much effort it took,

00:06:38.079 --> 00:06:39.079
and how many hardships I endured

00:06:39.240 --> 00:06:40.399
to get to where I am today.

00:06:40.680 --> 00:06:41.839
Your scheme seems clever,

00:06:42.279 --> 00:06:43.319
but it doesn't stand up to scrutiny.

00:06:44.319 --> 00:06:45.879
After you gained Zhao Qishan's trust,

00:06:47.040 --> 00:06:48.639
he relaxed his supervision of you slightly.

00:06:49.759 --> 00:06:51.519
You took the chance to establish contact with Li Ran

00:06:52.439 --> 00:06:53.959
and began looking for a way to escape.

00:06:57.720 --> 00:06:58.360
Sis,

00:06:58.920 --> 00:06:59.680
what is going on with you?

00:06:59.800 --> 00:07:00.959
You disappeared for months.

00:07:03.120 --> 00:07:04.879
Although your social media account is updating,

00:07:05.040 --> 00:07:06.319
I knew something was wrong as soon as I saw it.

00:07:07.600 --> 00:07:08.720
I'm really worried about you.

00:07:11.160 --> 00:07:12.120
What exactly is happening?

00:07:12.519 --> 00:07:13.079
Xiao Ran,

00:07:13.800 --> 00:07:14.680
calm down first.

00:07:16.279 --> 00:07:18.439
Remember every word I'm about to say.

00:07:21.879 --> 00:07:23.879
The victims you tricked or captured

00:07:24.759 --> 00:07:26.560
were all influencers traveling abroad alone.

00:07:27.439 --> 00:07:29.000
They were all good-looking women.

00:07:30.800 --> 00:07:32.639
Perhaps you already had a plan in mind,

00:07:33.560 --> 00:07:34.560
wanting to find

00:07:35.160 --> 00:07:37.240
a woman with a similar figure to be your double.

00:07:38.399 --> 00:07:39.079
Very soon,

00:07:40.639 --> 00:07:41.839
this candidate appeared.

00:07:55.480 --> 00:07:56.519
On the night of the crime,

00:07:57.160 --> 00:07:58.680
you sent the double to Zhao Qishan.

00:07:59.800 --> 00:08:00.399
You spread her DNA

00:08:00.560 --> 00:08:01.759
all over the room,

00:08:03.319 --> 00:08:05.199
thus beginning your revenge plan.